Re: overflow bug SERIOUS

Bitcointalk

2010-08-16 12:59:38 UTC - [11]Original Post

   It looks like we overtook the bad chain somewhere around 74689.  0.3.9
   and lower nodes have been responding with the current block number for
   some hours now.
   That means itʼs no longer necessary to delete blk*.dat before
   upgrading.  You can just upgrade and itʼll reorg away the bad block
   chain.
   Thanks to everyone for the quick response!
